column5: Im off to pops and moms for the weekend. Pop and I will be fishing the Huntsville Pike Tourney Sunday for a good cause to support the local Volunteer FF.  I,ll besure to post a report with lots of pic,s from the festive,s on Monday.  You all have great and safe weekend.
Give'm hell Brian !  We'll expect a FULL picture filled report by Monday noon !
good luck win lots of money    oh and have fun
Good luck Brian, I'll catch a couple of whities for ya!!  Rob
Have fun B.  Will you be fishing Doe at all this weekend?  Joey
He's signed off Joey!!!  Sorry couldn't resist!!  Rob

Ahhh Brian... I wish you luck.. I'm off to help celebrate my best friends 50th birthday party... a surprise, thrown by her daughter.... but I entend to wet a line in the Keswick or further north area, BEFORE I arrive.  ...  GOOD LUCK TO YA!!!!
Good luck in the tourney Brian. We'll be waiting for the pictures.
